Fishing boats tied up at Son Tra beach, with coastline highrises in the distance.
</p>
<p class="jp">    
<span class="title_jp">ソンチャー
</span>  
ソンチャー・ビーチに停泊する漁船と、遠くに見える海岸線の高層ビル群。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Vietnam" /><category term="Art" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Fishing boats tied up at Son Tra beach, with coastline highrises in the distance. ソンチャー ソンチャー・ビーチに停泊する漁船と、遠くに見える海岸線の高層ビル群。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00205_x.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00205_x.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hand in the Clouds</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251030/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hand in the Clouds" /><published>2025-10-30T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-30T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/bana-bridge</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251030/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The Golden "Hand" Bridge (Cầu Vàng) at Ba Na Hills in Da Nang. The park is almost a mile up into the mountains, and on this day was completely enclosed by clouds.
</p>
<p class="jp">    
<span class="title_jp">雲の中の手
</span>  
ダナンのバーナーヒルズにある「手」橋。この公園は山中の標高約1,500メートルにあり、この日は完全に雲に包まれていた。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Vietnam" /><category term="Art" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The Golden "Hand" Bridge (Cầu Vàng) at Ba Na Hills in Da Nang. The park is almost a mile up into the mountains, and on this day was completely enclosed by clouds. 雲の中の手 ダナンのバーナーヒルズにある「手」橋。この公園は山中の標高約1,500メートルにあり、この日は完全に雲に包まれていた。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00227.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00227.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Huyen Khong Cave</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251029/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Huyen Khong Cave" /><published>2025-10-29T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-29T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/marble-mountain</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251029/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A large buddha inside the Huyen Khong Cave, largest of dozen caves in Da Nang's Marble Mountains.
</p>
<p class="jp">    
<span class="title_jp">フエンコン洞窟
</span>  
ダナンのマーブルマウンテンにある十数か所の洞窟の中で最大のフエンコン洞窟内にある大きな仏像。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Vietnam" /><category term="Art" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A large buddha inside the Huyen Khong Cave, largest of dozen caves in Da Nang's Marble Mountains. フエンコン洞窟 ダナンのマーブルマウンテンにある十数か所の洞窟の中で最大のフエンコン洞窟内にある大きな仏像。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00217.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00217.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Da Nang Skyline</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251028/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Da Nang Skyline" /><published>2025-10-28T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-28T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/dan-nang-skyline</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251028/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Looking at the skyline of Da Nang, with the Bãi Bụt beach in the foreground.
</p>
<p class="jp">    
<span class="title_jp">ダナンのスカイライン
</span>  
バイ・ブット・ビーチを前景にダナンのスカイラインを見る。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Vietnam" /><category term="Views" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Rain" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking at the skyline of Da Nang, with the Bãi Bụt beach in the foreground. ダナンのスカイライン バイ・ブット・ビーチを前景にダナンのスカイラインを見る。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00195_x.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00195_x.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Vietnam Typhoon</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251026/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Vietnam Typhoon" /><published>2025-10-26T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-26T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/vietnam</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251026/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
First time in Vietnam and we were welcomed by Typhoon Fengshen, heavy rain and flooding. That did not stop the locals however, who simply donned their ponchos and continued on.
</p>
<p class="jp">    
<span class="title_jp">ベトナム台風</span>  
初めてのベトナムで、私たちは台風12号の大雨と洪水に見舞われた。しかし、それでも地元の人々はポンチョを着込み、そのまま進み続けた。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Vietnam" /><category term="Night" /><category term="Rain" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[First time in Vietnam and we were welcomed by Typhoon Fengshen, heavy rain and flooding. That did not stop the locals however, who simply donned their ponchos and continued on. ベトナム台風 初めてのベトナムで、私たちは台風12号の大雨と洪水に見舞われた。しかし、それでも地元の人々はポンチョを着込み、そのまま進み続けた。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00161.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00161.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Daikaku-ji Temple・大覚寺</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251025/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Daikaku-ji Temple・大覚寺" /><published>2025-10-25T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-25T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/daikakuji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251025/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Mie-do Hall at Daikaku-ji Temple the other day. Rendered on Fujicolor Superia 400 film.
</p>
<p class="jp">    
先日の大覚寺御影堂。富士フイルム スペリア400で撮影。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Daikaku-ji" /><category term="Film" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Mie-do Hall at Daikaku-ji Temple the other day. Rendered on Fujicolor Superia 400 film. 先日の大覚寺御影堂。富士フイルム スペリア400で撮影。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSC_1408-positive.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSC_1408-positive.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Bamboo Lightup・嵐山月灯路</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251024/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Bamboo Lightup・嵐山月灯路" /><published>2025-10-24T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-24T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/tsukitoro</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251024/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Visitor to an evening illumination event in Arashiyama's Bamboo Grove, takes a photo of illuminated hanging bamboo balls.
</p>
<p class="jp">    

嵐山の竹林で開催されたイルミネーションイベント「嵐山月灯路」で、来場者がライトアップされた吊り竹玉を撮影している。]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Bamboo Grove" /><category term="Night" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Visitor to an evening illumination event in Arashiyama's Bamboo Grove, takes a photo of illuminated hanging bamboo balls.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00144_x.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00144_x.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Boat on the River・屋形船</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251023/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Boat on the River・屋形船" /><published>2025-10-23T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-23T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/yakatabune</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251023/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A boatman, piloting his flat-bottomed boat with a long bamboo rod, returns downstream after dropping off his passengers. A couple enjoy the  river from the shore.
</p>
<p class="jp">    
長い竹竿で屋形船を操る船頭が下流へ向かう。岸辺から川遊びを楽しむカップル。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Boats" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A boatman, piloting his flat-bottomed boat with a long bamboo rod, returns downstream after dropping off his passengers. A couple enjoy the river from the shore. 長い竹竿で屋形船を操る船頭が下流へ向かう。岸辺から川遊びを楽しむカップル。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_IMG_2232_x.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_IMG_2232_x.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Music in the Grove・竹林の音楽</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251019/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Music in the Grove・竹林の音楽" /><published>2025-10-19T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-19T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/music-in-the-grove</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251019/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Shamisen player serenades visitors in Arashiyama's bamboo grove.</p>
<p class="jp">    
嵐山の竹林で三味線奏者が演奏している。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Bamboo Grove" /><category term="Black and White" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Shamisen player serenades visitors in Arashiyama's bamboo grove. 嵐山の竹林で三味線奏者が演奏している。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSCF1453.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSCF1453.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Togetsu Morning・渡月橋の朝</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251017/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Togetsu Morning・渡月橋の朝" /><published>2025-10-17T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-17T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/togetsu-morning</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251017/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Watching the morning sky from the Togetsukyo Bridge, as the sun emerges from behind the Higashiyama mountains in the east.
</p>
<p class="jp">    
渡月橋から朝の空を眺める。太陽が東山の向こうから顔を出し始める。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Dawn" /><category term="Sunrise" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Watching the morning sky from the Togetsukyo Bridge, as the sun emerges from behind the Higashiyama mountains in the east. 渡月橋から朝の空を眺める。太陽が東山の向こうから顔を出し始める。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00071-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_A7R00071-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>